      "parameters": {
        "content": "**🟢 Data Ingestion & Initial Screening**\n\n**📡 PHASE 1: DATA INGESTION**\n\n**Automated Triggering:** Initiates every 60 seconds via a scheduled interval for continuous monitoring.\n**Telemetry Retrieval:** Fetches real-time sensor data (Temp, Vibration, Pressure) via REST API.\nData Pre-Processing: Custom JavaScript sanitizes raw JSON and calculates Trend Deltas.\nHeuristic Screening: Performs a low-latency check to flag immediate outliers before AI processing.\n",
