      "parameters": {
        "content": "**🔵 Intelligent Logic & Routing**\n\n**⚖️ PHASE 2: INTELLIGENT ROUTING**\n\n• Threshold Evaluation: Compares live readings against Safety Compliance Standards (e.g., Critical > 87°C).\n• Dynamic Path Allocation:\n\n🔴 Emergency: Immediate AI diagnostic & high-priority alerting.\n\n🟡 Warning: Cautionary logging for maintenance review.\n\n🟢 Normal: Routine archival with zero alarm interference.",
