        "content": "**🟠 AI Diagnostic & Dispatch**\n\n**🧠 PHASE 3: AI DIAGNOSTIC ENGINE**\n\nRoot-Cause Analysis: The LLM Agent interprets correlations (e.g., High Vibration + High Temp) to predict mechanical failure.\nOmni-Channel Alerting: Dispatches instant alerts to Slack (Engineering) and SMTP (Management).\nVisual Reporting: Generates a professional HTML Report with embedded AI insights for immediate decision-making.\n\n",
