        "content": "**🔴 Data Archival & System Feedback**\n\n**📊 PHASE 4: ARCHIVAL & HANDSHAKE**\n\nPermanent Logging: Records all incident data into Google Sheets for Audit Trails and Trend Analysis.\nData Filtering: Uses post-process filters to ensure only validated anomalies are archived.\nExecution Handshake: Closes the loop via Webhook Response, providing a JSON 200 OK status to the trigger source.",
