      "parameters": {
        "content": "**🛡️ PHASE 5: SYSTEM HEALTH**\n\nFail-Safe Monitoring: Autonomously watches all 28 nodes for any execution failures or timeouts.\nInstant Admin Alert: In case of a system crash, an emergency notification is dispatched to the administrator.\nSystem Integrity: Ensures refinery monitoring remains active by flagging issues immediately.",
