    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "**🛡️ SENTINEL-AI: INDUSTRIAL REFINERY MONITORING SYSTEM**\n\nSentinel-AI is a sophisticated, autonomous framework designed for high-precision infrastructure monitoring. It transforms raw sensor telemetry into actionable industrial intelligence by bridging the gap between Real-Time Data Acquisition and Generative AI Diagnostics.\n\n**🛠️ CORE ARCHITECTURE**\nThe system is divided into four critical operational phases:\n\nIngestion: High-frequency polling of industrial sensors (Temp, Vibration, Pressure).\n\nLogic & Routing: Intelligent triage that classifies data into Emergency, Warning, or Routine status.\n\nAI Diagnostics: Root-cause analysis powered by an LLM Agent to identify mechanical trends and potential failures.\n\nOmni-Channel Response: Simultaneous alerting via Slack and SMTP, with long-term archival in Google Sheets.\n\n**🧠 SYSTEM CAPABILITIES**\nPredictive Maintenance: Moves beyond simple threshold alerts to \"Trend Analysis.\"\n\nAutonomous Decision-Making: Routes critical data to specialized AI models without manual intervention.\n\nAudit-Ready Logging: Maintains a 100% transparent history for regulatory compliance.\n\nFail-Safe Integrity: Integrated Phase 5 (Error Handler) ensures zero-downtime monitoring.\n\n**Status:** v1.0.0 Production-Ready\n**Developer:** Ansa\n**Project Type:** Industrial IoT / AI Automation",
